name: Mirage
description:
Some places are mirages. Do they
exist? Am I alive? // Pipe dreams, a
sweet, blue, vivid delusion. Transient
feelings shaped in desires, echoes of
identity or Ego? // A land of illusions,
chasing hopes, what ifs & could be.
From distant, mirror of a daydream;
from close, reflection of self. I am the
mirage.
